<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>sakavarṣa 1162 neya sārvvari saṁvatsarada puśyada Amavā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>se Ādivāradaṁdu śrīmatu sarvvādhikāri bhāgubāyi<unclear>ga</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḷu śrīvijayāpurada śrīnarasiṁhadēvara Āṁgabhōga naṁ<unclear>dā</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dīvige tadarttavāgi Uṁbaravāṇiya nīlādēviya gade 1 kaṭṭe
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yakeya mattaru 3 nāvidigeyavara sthaḷada horeyalu matta
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ru 2 A(ṁ)nu mattaru 5 Āvūra gavigiya baḷiya mane 1 vija
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yāpuradalliyā narasiṁgadēvarige gāṇa 1 Antu Anitu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>maṁ sarvvanamasyavāgi dhārāpūrvvakaṁ māḍikoṭṭa<unclear>ru</unclear>
<lb n="9"/>Ā gāṇada vokaliṁ<unclear>ge</unclear> kaḍāya bi<unclear>ṭṭi</unclear> mukhya kiṟukuḷa pakāradeṟe sarvvābādha pari
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> vuṁbaravāṇiya dēvara kaṁmatada kabbukaḷame bhatagamata bāḍukāyi
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṁda vinubāhaḍaṁ suṁkaparihāra 
</p>

